  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4894290">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4894290/" class="title-link">读《古学经子》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4894290"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/danyboy/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1186285-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/danyboy/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">danyboy</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-04-05"
      class="main-meta">2011-04-05 19:13:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4894290_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书不是经学子学概论，不知道为什么很多人都说这是本概论呢，这是本读书札记，以提出并解释自己读书时遇到的问题为主，只是文章确实有一些“述”的部分，正如作者在后记所说，“由读书札记汇辑而成，多为述学之言”，才被看做是“概论”，其实读此书还是抱着读学术笔记的目...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4894290/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">13有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4894290_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4894290_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2332879">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2332879/" class="title-link">简明的一部经学子学著述</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2332879"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1612030/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1612030-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1612030/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">米奇爱书</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-09-14"
      class="main-meta">2009-09-14 19:00:38</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2332879_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      王氏不知其所来，北大有美学教师同名，不知是一人否？ 此书言简意赅，取舍恰当。以每经籍单书为小题，据各书之难点逐次讲解。譬如易经以传承为难，故重点讲授传承之次序。尚书以真伪为要，故重点别明篇章之时段蕴意。特别之处乃是能脱离古文经学之藩篱，发今文经学之承传脉...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2332879/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2332879_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2332879_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





